":1970602,"uid":51920,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"59247d6faa905a61bf1ee097f8a0aa3ae51a2a46","tid":1970602,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T09:17:21.000Z","msg":"2020-04-13 16:29<br />\n<br />\n郵輪業業務和股價因「鑽石公主號」（Diamond Princess）等郵輪相繼爆發武漢肺炎疫情而受重創，但有數據顯示，2021年的郵輪行程預訂量，約在過去1個月出現增漲。圖為紅寶石公主號（Ruby Princess）。（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕郵輪業業務和股價因「鑽石公主號」（Diamond Princess）等郵輪相繼爆發武漢肺炎疫情而受重創，但有數據顯示，2021年的郵輪預訂量，在過去1個月出現增長，<a href=\"http://以郵輪預訂網站CruiseCompete.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%BB%A5%E9%83%B5%E8%BC%AA%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%82%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99CruiseCompete.com&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWW9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=bf620106\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">以郵輪預訂網站CruiseCompete.com</a>而言，其明年郵輪行程過去45天以來的預定量，和2019年相比增加40％，顯示郵輪業並未因疫情而完全流失其客戶。<br />\n<br />\n《Businessinsider》今（13）報導，<a href=\"http://郵輪預訂網站CruiseCompete.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E9%83%B5%E8%BC%AA%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%82%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99CruiseCompete.com&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWW9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=afb430b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">郵輪預訂網站CruiseCompete.com</a>和瑞士銀行（UBS）數據都顯示，即使郵輪業受武漢肺炎疫情重大衝擊，民眾並未完全失去對郵輪旅行的興趣。據《洛杉磯時報》（Los Angeles Times）報導，約在過去45天，<a href=\"http://CruiseCompete.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FCruiseCompete.com&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWW9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=cfadf3ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">CruiseCompete.com</a>的2021年郵輪行程預訂量，和2019年相比增加了40％。<br />\n<br />\n而據英國《泰晤士報》（The Times），瑞銀最近的分析發現，約在過去30天中，2021年的郵輪預訂量與今年同期相比，增長了9％，其中不只有重新預訂已取消的郵輪行程，還包括大量對新郵輪行程的預定。且在2020年取消行程的客戶中，有76％選擇接受2021年行程的代金券，選擇退款者則約達24%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://另據郵輪評論網站CruiseCritic.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%8F%A6%E6%93%9A%E9%83%B5%E8%BC%AA%E8%A9%95%E8%AB%96%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99CruiseCritic.com&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWW9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=c2bdaf04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">另據郵輪評論網站CruiseCritic.com</a>對4600名郵輪客戶進行調查的結果，顯示有75％的受訪者表示，在武漢肺炎疫情平息後，其郵輪旅行的次數將和過去相同，而有24％的受訪者表示，其有計畫減少預訂遊輪行程的次數。<br />\n<br />\n且雖然嘉年華郵輪公司（Carnival Cruise Corporation）旗下的鑽石公主號和紅寶石公主號（Ruby Princess），為兩艘疫情爆發規模最大的郵輪，並使該公司股價一度暴跌80％，但郵輪業似乎漸受年輕投資人青睞，美國德美利證券（TD Ameritrade）市場策略長JJ Kinahan曾在本月初指出，該公司的千禧世代投資人，約在3月的最後2週內，開始增持郵輪公司皇家加勒比（Royal Caribbean）和嘉年華集團的股票。<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3132030\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3132030&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWW9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=d0dd172a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3132030&h=f76b1e3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3132030</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T09:19:45.000Z","msg":"Ccl 點解仲跌？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T09:24:20.000Z","msg":"Priced in 左啦"},{"pid":"3978579ed6e52621372db9263300f5c76de6d1ae","tid":1970602,"uid":170297,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T09:27:16.000Z","msg":"乜撚都報復性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1c7b59d2811377023a1fbb4077493e0ad80dea5","tid":1970602,"uid":134128,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T09:30:53.000Z","msg":"財演收左錢叫傻散入貨  俾大戶走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63b30b5e60d1f1d7dbb0f59e468e6e13d06523b9","tid":1970602,"uid":132137,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T09:37:37.000Z","msg":"一定無人坐"},{"pid":"126f444be4bdbe297315cdc5e9c2c501b13e0217","tid":1970602,"uid":257491,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T09:39:12.000Z","msg":"之後排華 仲旅遊 遊你條毛咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8493b2be1c976c7e0c135e20343212f64e31f7e",